p: According to the PASS estimates presented in Table 1, Table 2, Table 3, Table 4, Table 5, Table 6, Table 7, Table 8, Table 9, Table 10 and Table 11, many endoperoxides demonstrate antitumor and related activities to varying degrees. Figure 14 demonstrates natural compounds and their predicted antitumor activity with Pa > 95%.
